        "id": 11964
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-05-18T13:37:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I like the idea of a builder, but when it comes to resource IDs I meant that we just move\n InputStream is \u003d getResources().openRawResource(id);\n byte[] data \u003d new byte[is.available()];\n is.read(data);\n\nto AndroidKit\u0027s Java code. So it becomes:\n mAnimation \u003d new SkotieAnimation(R.raw.im_thirsty);\n\nWe can leave that until later though.",
      "parentUuid": "044fff9c_61493b41",
      "revId": "6c97c39895067e3252daf1762714a86aff85e369",
